{"tid":1745334,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]FFBE WOTV 幻影戰爭(4) 新pool引岀歐洲人","createTime":"2019-11-22T07:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:13:06.000Z","uid":36980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0ac0065e2b0bfa18ef43df12bcd3e4de2c8210","tid":1745334,"uid":36980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"由 SQUARE ENIX + Gumi 開發，預計在 2019 年於 Android／iOS 雙平台所推出的戰棋 RPG 新作《FFBE 幻影戰爭 WAR OF THE VISIONS》（原名：WAR OF THE VISIONS ファイナルファンタジー ブレイブエクスヴィアス 幻影戦争）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">trailer</span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QHP5elZS41w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQHP5elZS41w&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=b2bbcfe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QHP5elZS41w</a><br />\n\t<br />\n本作（以下簡稱為《幻影戰爭》）是《Final Fantasy》系列的戰棋 RPG 新作，故事舞台在阿拉德大陸上，自古以來有著關於水晶的傳說，為了爭奪這片土地的霸權而展開了一場被後人稱為「幻影戰爭」的故事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ArjR2st.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FArjR2st.jpg&h=3c25b963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《幻影戰爭》的戰鬥系統上傳承了《Final Fantasy Tactics》的戰棋系統，地形明顯的高低差能夠影響敵我雙方的移動力以及戰力，搭配上多變化的角色職業更增加了戰略要素，而配合手機遊戲玩家所設計的自動模式與倍速模式，即使是第一次接觸戰棋遊戲的初學者都能輕鬆上手。不同角色的必殺技跟能力與強力的召喚獸都會以 3D 動畫的華麗演出來呈現。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲畫面</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5S0VNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5S0VNV.jpg&h=252c9401&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDpywmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDpywmg.jpg&h=19fbcf89&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5eww2sW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5eww2sW.jpg&h=14178f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於熟悉《FF》系列的玩家來說，多樣化的職業系統當然不可少，這次《幻影戰爭》有著豪華聲優陣容擔任配音的故事任務以外，也將有世界任務與活動任務等多樣化的關卡讓玩家挑戰，還有多人任務、副本與 PVP 對戰等要素包含其中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOenpGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOenpGF.jpg&h=7df0d3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VAqntm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VAqntm.jpg&h=d9bb632a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXorRmG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXorRmG.jpg&h=5aa49e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1A1XX1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1A1XX1H.jpg&h=277cd44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.square_enix.WOTVffbejp&amp;referrer=utm_source%3Dgamer.com.tw%26utm_campaign%3Dgnn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.square_enix.WOTVffbejp%26referrer%3Dutm_source%253Dgamer.com.tw%2526utm_campaign%253Dgnn&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=66c2b964\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.square_enix.WOTVffbejp&amp;referrer=utm_source%3Dgamer.com.tw%26utm_campaign%3Dgnn</a><br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1443703517?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1443703517%3Fmt%3D8&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyljMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=ba8107ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1443703517?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n人物/勢力關係圖<br />\n一圖睇晒故事背景+第1-2章劇情<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDtTJ0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDtTJ0B.jpg&h=9dbe5f7d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}